      <title>力扣题解：最长连续序列</title>
      <link href="/2026/04/18/zui-chang-lian-xu-xu-lie/"/>
      <url>/2026/04/18/zui-chang-lian-xu-xu-lie/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="🧠-力扣题解：最长连续序列"><a href="#🧠-力扣题解：最长连续序列" class="headerlink" title="🧠 力扣题解：最长连续序列"></a>🧠 力扣题解：最长连续序列</h1><h2 id="🔗-题目链接"><a href="#🔗-题目链接" class="headerlink" title="🔗 题目链接"></a>🔗 题目链接</h2><p><a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/longest-consecutive-sequence/description/?envType=study-plan-v2&envId=top-100-liked">点击查看题目</a></p><hr><h2 id="🧩-解题思路"><a href="#🧩-解题思路" class="headerlink" title="🧩 解题思路"></a>🧩 解题思路</h2><p>整体思路：先把所有数字放进哈希集合，之后只从“连续序列起点”出发向后扩展，统计每段连续长度并更新最大值。</p><ol><li>先定义 <code>unordered_set&lt;int&gt; nset</code>，并把 <code>nums</code> 里的所有元素插入进去。</li></ol><ul><li>这样做的目的，是把“某个数字是否存在”的查询变成近似 O(1)。</li><li>同时集合会自动去重，避免重复数字影响连续长度统计。</li></ul><ol start="2"><li><p>定义 <code>longest = 0</code>，用于记录目前找到的最长连续长度。</p></li><li><p>遍历 <code>nset</code> 中的每个 <code>num</code>，判断它是不是某段连续序列的起点。</p></li></ol><ul><li>条件是 <code>if(!nset.count(num - 1))</code>。</li><li>如果 <code>num - 1</code> 不存在，说明 <code>num</code> 前面接不上更小的连续数字，它就是起点。</li><li>如果 <code>num - 1</code> 存在，就跳过，因为这段序列会在更小的起点处被统计到。</li></ul><ol start="4"><li>对每个起点开始向后扩展。</li></ol><ul><li>先设 <code>cur = num</code>，<code>curlong = 1</code>。</li><li>当 <code>nset.count(cur + 1)</code> 为真时，不断执行：<ul><li><code>cur += 1</code></li><li><code>curlong += 1</code></li></ul></li><li>这段 <code>while</code> 的作用是把以 <code>num</code> 开头的连续序列完整走一遍。</li></ul><ol start="5"><li>每统计完一段连续序列，更新答案。</li></ol><ul><li><code>longest = max(longest, curlong)</code>。</li><li>最后返回 <code>longest</code>。</li></ul><p>关键设计在于“只从起点扩展”这一点：每个数字最多被向后访问一次，避免了重复扫描，保证了整体效率。</p><hr><h2 id="⏱️-复杂度分析"><a href="#⏱️-复杂度分析" class="headerlink" title="⏱️ 复杂度分析"></a>⏱️ 复杂度分析</h2><h3 id="时间复杂度"><a href="#时间复杂度" class="headerlink" title="时间复杂度"></a>时间复杂度</h3><ul><li><strong>O(n)</strong></li><li>解释：<ul><li>把数组插入集合是 O(n)。</li><li>遍历集合是 O(n)。</li><li>虽然有 <code>while</code>，但由于只从起点扩展，每个数字最多被扩展访问一次，总体仍是 O(n)。</li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="空间复杂度"><a href="#空间复杂度" class="headerlink" title="空间复杂度"></a>空间复杂度</h3><ul><li><strong>O(n)</strong></li><li>额外使用了 <code>unordered_set</code> 存储所有数字，空间开销与输入规模线性相关。</li></ul><hr><h2 id="💻-代码（必须放在结尾）"><a href="#💻-代码（必须放在结尾）" class="headerlink" title="💻 代码（必须放在结尾）"></a>💻 代码（必须放在结尾）</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">longestConsecutive</span><span class="params">(vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&amp; nums)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        unordered_set&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; nset;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span>&amp;num : nums)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            nset.<span class="built_in">insert</span>(num);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> longest=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">int</span> &amp; num : nset)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(!nset.<span class="built_in">count</span>(num<span class="number">-1</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="type">int</span> cur = num;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="type">int</span> curlong = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">while</span>(nset.<span class="built_in">count</span>(cur<span class="number">+1</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    cur+=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                    curlong+=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">                longest=<span class="built_in">max</span>(longest,curlong);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> longest;         </span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
