      <title>力扣题解：两数之和</title>
      <link href="/2026/04/17/liang-shu-zhi-he/"/>
      <url>/2026/04/17/liang-shu-zhi-he/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="力扣题解：两数之和"><a href="#力扣题解：两数之和" class="headerlink" title="力扣题解：两数之和"></a>力扣题解：两数之和</h1><h2 id="题目链接"><a href="#题目链接" class="headerlink" title="题目链接"></a>题目链接</h2><p><a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/two-sum/description/?envType=study-plan-v2&envId=top-100-liked">点击查看题目</a></p><hr><h2 id="解题思路"><a href="#解题思路" class="headerlink" title="解题思路"></a>解题思路</h2><p>这段代码的核心思路是：<strong>一边遍历数组，一边用哈希表记录已经出现过的数字和它的下标，同时检查当前数字需要的配对值是否已经出现</strong>。</p><ol><li><p>先定义哈希表 <code>mp</code>，类型是 <code>unordered_map&lt;int, int&gt;</code>。<br>作用是记录“数字 -&gt; 下标”的映射，表示这个数字在前面出现过。</p></li><li><p>用 <code>for</code> 循环从左到右遍历 <code>nums</code>，当前下标为 <code>i</code>。<br>每次先计算 <code>x = target - nums[i]</code>，<code>x</code> 表示当前数字还需要的另一个值。</p></li><li><p>通过 <code>mp.count(x)</code> 判断 <code>x</code> 是否已经在前面出现。<br>如果出现，直接返回 <code>{mp[x], i}</code>，分别是之前那个数的下标和当前下标。</p></li><li><p>如果没找到，就把当前数字存入哈希表：<code>mp[nums[i]] = i</code>，供后续元素匹配。</p></li><li><p>最后 <code>return vector&lt;int&gt;();</code> 作为兜底返回。</p></li></ol><p>关键设计点：</p><ul><li>先查找再插入，避免当前元素和自己配对。</li><li>哈希表把“查找某个数是否出现过”从线性优化到均摊常数时间。</li></ul><hr><h2 id="复杂度分析"><a href="#复杂度分析" class="headerlink" title="复杂度分析"></a>复杂度分析</h2><h3 id="时间复杂度"><a href="#时间复杂度" class="headerlink" title="时间复杂度"></a>时间复杂度</h3><p><code>O(n)</code>。</p><p>数组只遍历一遍，循环 <code>n</code> 次。每次哈希查找&#x2F;插入均摊 <code>O(1)</code>，所以总时间复杂度是 <code>O(n)</code>。</p><h3 id="空间复杂度"><a href="#空间复杂度" class="headerlink" title="空间复杂度"></a>空间复杂度</h3><p><code>O(n)</code>。</p><p>额外使用哈希表存储遍历过的元素，最坏情况下需要存近 <code>n</code> 个键值对。</p><hr><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Solution</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt; <span class="title">twoSum</span><span class="params">(vector&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;&amp; nums, <span class="type">int</span> target)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        unordered_map&lt;<span class="type">int</span>,<span class="type">int</span>&gt; mp;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; nums.<span class="built_in">size</span>(); i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">int</span> x = target - nums[i];</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (mp.<span class="built_in">count</span>(x)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span> &#123;mp[x], i&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            mp[nums[i]] = i;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">vector</span>&lt;<span class="type">int</span>&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 分享 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
